- Platform: iOS
- Language: Swift
- UI Framework: SwiftUI
- Data Persistence: SwiftData
- `UserDefaults` for simple settings like reminder time.
- Notifications: `UserNotifications` using local ios notifications for local reminders.
- Architecture:  MVVM (Model-View-ViewModel)
- Minimum iOS Version: 17+
- Privacy: All data will be stored locally on the user's device. No cloud sync or external data transmission. A clear privacy statement should be available.
- to build and check for errors use platform: iOS Simulator, arch:arm64, name:iPhone 16 Plus